WHO   — The Economy — wildcards · gems · the grind
WHAT  — The pay-to-FAST engine: money accelerates a collection rather than buying wins, with draft as the great skill-equaliser.
WHERE — MTG · MTG Arena  Framework inputs: Magic: The Gathering / MTG Arena (WotC)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
