HOW   — By packs and wildcards, daily quests and ranked rewards, and the constant pull between grinding and paying.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am pay-to-fast, not pay-to-win — money buys you the collection sooner, but draft will still humble you on pure skill.

